95586ab1-fa6c-4268-8fb4-b9450c067cd5.title: Fred The Farmer
95586ab1-fa6c-4268-8fb4-b9450c067cd5.text:
What are you doing on my land? You're not the one
who keeps leaving my gates open and letting out all
my sheep are you?

options.text: I'm looking for something to kill.

b0f0f87f-971d-467e-b350-39e7dbd5433a.title: Fred The Farmer
b0f0f87f-971d-467e-b350-39e7dbd5433a.text:
You're after a quest you say? Actually I could do with
a bit of help.

1140e6a8-a6c0-442d-8816-60a9e38bcfd0.title: Fred The Farmer
1140e6a8-a6c0-442d-8816-60a9e38bcfd0.text:
My sheep are getting mighty wooly. I'd be much
obliged if you could shear them. And while you're at it
spin the wool for me too.

3b700810-8280-46df-8459-06cc7746eff5.title: Fred The Farmer
3b700810-8280-46df-8459-06cc7746eff5.text:
Yes, thats it. Bring me 20 balls of wool. And I'm sure
I could sort out some sort of payment. Of course,
there's the small matter of The Thing.

options.text: Yes okay. I can do that.
That doesn't sound a very exciting quest.
What do you mean, The Thing?

68491c88-9bc5-41b0-994b-8af82f375bee.title: <player>
68491c88-9bc5-41b0-994b-8af82f375bee.text: Yes okay. I can do that.

a2fbdb8a-3968-4312-81b9-28adb726ff65.title: <player>
a2fbdb8a-3968-4312-81b9-28adb726ff65.text: That doesn't sound a very exciting quest.

4de7d9cb-867a-4167-b7bb-857623d2db44.title: Fred The Farmer
4de7d9cb-867a-4167-b7bb-857623d2db44.text:
Well what do you expect if you ask a farmer for a
quest? Now are you going to help me or not?

options.text: Yes okay. I can do that.
No I'll give it a miss.

ad5227e1-6a62-4247-b499-60cafdf5cd1e.title: <player>
ad5227e1-6a62-4247-b499-60cafdf5cd1e.text: What do you mean, The Thing?

531efb5f-1faa-4145-a324-4533b14ece7a.title: <player>
531efb5f-1faa-4145-a324-4533b14ece7a.text: No I'll give it a miss.

1e4b4cd3-e097-4844-b659-7f519bb22ee0.title: Fred The Farmer
1e4b4cd3-e097-4844-b659-7f519bb22ee0.text:
Well now, no one has ever seend The Thing. That's
why we call it The Thing, 'cos we don't know what it is.

46cd6ba1-77ba-42ff-85e3-fb89b57679a2.title: Fred The Farmer
46cd6ba1-77ba-42ff-85e3-fb89b57679a2.text:
Some say it's a black hearted shapeshifter, hungering for
the souls of the hard working decent folk like me. Others
say it's just a sheep.

0270a5da-a1b2-4a1b-97bc-03907d1598e6.title: Fred The Farmer
0270a5da-a1b2-4a1b-97bc-03907d1598e6.text:
Well I don't have all day to stand around and gossip.
Are you going to shear my sheep or what!

options.text: Yes okay. I can do that.
Erm I'm  a bit worried about this Thing.

f3c743d0-f8ff-49b2-865e-5a240238ba8e.title: <player>
f3c743d0-f8ff-49b2-865e-5a240238ba8e.text: Erm I'm a bit worried about this Thing.

a3ecd86b-16a5-4cf4-9111-70193b4afab7.title: Fred The Farmer
a3ecd86b-16a5-4cf4-9111-70193b4afab7.text:
I'm sure it's nothing to worry about. Just because my
last shearer was seen bolting out of the field screaming
for his life doesn't mean anything.

51c3a547-2b24-4f48-86e7-900a8c5405de.title: <player>
51c3a547-2b24-4f48-86e7-900a8c5405de.text: I'm looking for something to kill.

46f0a50e-9ac7-46db-9420-4582036b7fc3.title: Fred The Farmer
46f0a50e-9ac7-46db-9420-4582036b7fc3.text:
What, on my land? Leave my livestock alone you
scoundrel!

571089ff-f332-4ef9-97a8-a60a686456b7.title: Fred The Farmer
571089ff-f332-4ef9-97a8-a60a686456b7.text:
How can you be lost? Just follow the road east and
south. You'll end up in Lumbridge fairly quickly.

6e6131b4-1a68-49b8-ae4b-46d09395241f.title: Fred The Farmer
6e6131b4-1a68-49b8-ae4b-46d09395241f.text: How are you doing getting those balls of wool?"

4958c135-fce2-4466-83f0-2d0c045e3093.title: <player>
4958c135-fce2-4466-83f0-2d0c045e3093.text: That's all I've got so far.

9882dbc0-a0b7-4bb7-8e15-c9aa15ac75a4.title: Fred The Farmer
9882dbc0-a0b7-4bb7-8e15-c9aa15ac75a4.text: I need <sheep_shearer_remaining> more before I can pay you.

1cb683c3-4237-49f0-b0b2-cb5dc05f83f7.title: Fred The Farmer
1cb683c3-4237-49f0-b0b2-cb5dc05f83f7.text: I guess I'd better pay you then.

45430058-a729-44cd-9848-bf483e68cd89.title: Fred The Farmer
45430058-a729-44cd-9848-bf483e68cd89.text: How are you doing getting those balls of wool?

f043f545-4e35-40a8-8ae2-a69380a9e161.title: <player>
f043f545-4e35-40a8-8ae2-a69380a9e161.text: How many more do I need to give you?

a83f9b2c-2ded-481f-9c0f-6584f4fbc79d.title: Fred The Farmer
a83f9b2c-2ded-481f-9c0f-6584f4fbc79d.text: You need to collect <sheep_shearer_remaining> more balls of wool.

a71fec03-ff07-4259-8850-1b11457015e5.title: <player>
a71fec03-ff07-4259-8850-1b11457015e5.text:
Well I've got some wool. I've not managed to make it
into a ball though.

50220ef5-b26f-4cb5-9e2b-70ac917096eb.title: Fred The Farmer
50220ef5-b26f-4cb5-9e2b-70ac917096eb.text:
Well go find a spinning wheel then. You can find one
on the first floor of the Lumbridge Castle, just walk east on
the road outside my house and you'll find Lumbridge.

e3bfe773-fdb3-4604-a10c-64ff5e982d23.title: <player>
e3bfe773-fdb3-4604-a10c-64ff5e982d23.text: I haven't got any at the moment.

cd500077-68ac-4c7d-8df6-3f789b6ef17b.title: Fred The Farmer
cd500077-68ac-4c7d-8df6-3f789b6ef17b.text: Ah well at least you haven't bene eaten.
